<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Wellness Clinic - Our Services</title>
    <style>
        /* Body styles */
        body {
            font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #ece9e6, #ffffff);
            color: #222;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Header styles */
        header {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff7e5f, #feb47b);
            color: white;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 0;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        /* Main content styles */
        main {
            padding: 2.5rem;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 3rem auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        /* Footer styles */
        footer {
            background-color: #222;
            color: #ddd;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        footer p {
            margin: 0;
        }

        /* Card styles */
        .appointment-card,
        .offering-card,
        .testimonial-card {
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin: 1.5rem 0;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .appointment-card:hover,
        .offering-card:hover,
        .testimonial-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 18px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .unavailable {
            opacity: 0.7;
            background-color: #ffe6e6;
            border: 1px solid #ffcccc;
        }

        .unavailable-text {
            color: #d32f2f;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        /* Grid styles */
        .testimonial-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        .testimonial-card {
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .testimonial-card:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Welcome to Wellness Clinic</h1>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section>
            <h2>Our Offerings</h2>
            <div class="offering-card">
                <h3>Full Body Massage</h3>
                <p><strong>Price:</strong> ₹2,500</p>
                <p><strong>Duration:</strong> 60 minutes</p>
                <p>Experience relaxation with our expert therapists using aromatic oils.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="offering-card unavailable">
                <h3>Detox Therapy</h3>
                <p><strong>Price:</strong> ₹3,500</p>
                <p><strong>Duration:</strong> 90 minutes</p>
                <p>Revitalize your body with our signature detox treatment.</p>
                <div class="unavailable-text">
                    <p>Currently Unavailable</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="offering-card">
                <h3>Yoga Sessions</h3>
                <p><strong>Price:</strong> ₹1,200</p>
                <p><strong>Duration:</strong> 45 minutes</p>
                <p>Join our guided yoga sessions to enhance flexibility and calmness.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2025 Wellness Clinic. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
